content: Sewer Gas Inside Cabin

Forest River, Inc. (Forest River) is recalling certain 2025 Coachmen Brookstone BKF398MBL fifth wheels.  The wastewater holding tank pipe may not extend to the exterior of the vehicle, allowing sewer gas to enter the cabin.Sewer gas inside the cabin increases the risk of injury.

Number of Units Affected: 23.0"
